          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "There is an issue I ran into while playing although I’m not sure if there’s any plan to fix it in a future update: In order to progress from an area, you must upgrade your phone with SIM cards hidden throughout the levels. Two thirds of the way through the game, I had found that area’s SIM card but it wouldn’t let me pass through that area’s exit door. Hopefully this gets patched post-launch. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
